    "# Churn Analysis — CART, C4.5 & Neural Network\n",
    "### Exercises 1–14 | MIT-Style Clean Implementation\n",
    "---\n",
    "**Models:** CART (Gini) · C4.5 (Entropy) · MLP Neural Network  \n",
    "**Topics:** Decision Trees · Confusion Matrix · Cost-Benefit · Lift & Gains · Model Comparison\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Imports"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
